cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.CG 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with non-rigid reconstruction using RGB-D camera and proposes a novel approach for foreground tracking. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper discusses camera pose estimation and tracking, which are important topics in robotics. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is another possible category as the paper deals with 3D reconstruction and deformation graph, which are relevant to computer graphics. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with RGB-D camera and reconstruction, which are relevant to multimedia applications. 
- cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is another possible category as the paper deals with 3D reconstruction and deformation graph, which are relevant to computational geometry.
